{"tid":419074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真] 好想了解下死亡、死後、靈魂之類","createTime":"2017-09-30T06:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T08:27:25.000Z","uid":79353,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bfc0695543ce379f3352c9d7547c96c9e838f23e","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以講下<br />\n<br />\n而家呢一刻最想知就係<br />\n人死左之後可唔可以拒絕輪迴<br />\n可唔可以係街上周圍飄然之後跟蹤想見既人?<br />\n<br />\n我好認真問，非膠PO，想討論下<br />\n<br />\n利申 咩都唔識"},{"pid":"f91d6141238fb8e29fe44609045c290f92f6a5eb","tid":419074,"uid":31208,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:56:38.000Z","msg":"生物粒子回歸塵土"},{"pid":"6237f81f048f962d7ec72718ea1c2a0ec2921d26","tid":419074,"uid":135408,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:57:00.000Z","msg":"成左佛就脫離生死輪迴<br />\n所以樓主做多啲好事啦"},{"pid":"0c95406ef684258bcb3cfe356a4938b718a068f2","tid":419074,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"究竟出面啲遊魂野鬼點嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e149d982a4ced4fc4c18c4d42b1ba952f8c9ee","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生物粒子回歸塵土</blockquote><br />\n人死左之後係咪真係冇晒任何感覺 意識 思想"},{"pid":"14f5b8ad82d8d88cdf5ccc7673929c7154e2824f","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成左佛就脫離生死輪迴<br />\n所以樓主做多啲好事啦</blockquote><br />\n有冇可能成到佛<br />\n又唔係醫生護士救人<br />\n<br />\n點先為之好事<br />\n計你內心念頭 定係 做出黎？"},{"pid":"832f75a21c0921ff8b9fade4f5a7e14af2213bc4","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T06:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>究竟出面啲遊魂野鬼點嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想知<br />\n係咪可以跟蹤朋友"},{"pid":"7516f02d89f6563a8e1bc59c19e2a18f4b5f019c","tid":419074,"uid":86740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:03:13.000Z","msg":"咁多鬼 條街咪越嚟越迫？"},{"pid":"e95718f2ca95e9964ed35c1c13cc50b60d78f579","tid":419074,"uid":134474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"跟蹤完想見嘅人又點，佢終有一日都會死<br />\n而你就繼續留戀人世四處飄泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 當世界上所有生前你識嘅人都瓜哂，巴打仲認為有機會會喺街度遇到佢地嘅靈魂咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cdf1ab045e6b42c96563ded253c714597ace406","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:04:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多鬼 條街咪越嚟越迫？</blockquote><br />\n你識茅山術？<br />\n<br />\n但實體人類又唔會踩到／阻到鬼？<br />\n<br />\n點計都係人怕鬼多過鬼怕人啦<br />\n<br />\n另外我聽講那個世界都係弱肉強食，真的嗎？"},{"pid":"6f6b971a59bcab3a84273e74e0d15594d08ca89e","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跟蹤完想見嘅人又點，佢終有一日都會死<br />\n而你就繼續留戀人世四處飄泊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 當世界上所有生前你識嘅人都瓜哂，巴打仲認為有機會會喺街度遇到佢地嘅靈魂咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人在生果陣都鍾意去旅行<br />\n而家好多人都唔參加旅遊團，鍾意自己執行李拎少少錢就出發去玩<br />\n就係鍾意呢種自由，唔洗跟人地俾的plan<br />\n<br />\n如果可以係呢個世界飄黎飄去，見證人間一千年之後會變成點<br />\n咁閱歷真係勁過我和殭屍有個約會隻天佑"},{"pid":"587b5b6cbb9c5898d0e66701be5708aa10756256","tid":419074,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"千萬不要自殺"},{"pid":"f7fa59ed9243428df5ab332f74ac235784484eb2","tid":419074,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千萬不要自殺</blockquote><br />\n唔會<br />\n<br />\n呢個問題我係Ｎew age討論<br />\n求其搵D宗教forum睇過下<br />\n<br />\n人就算自殺死左，都唔可以周圍跟蹤想見既人"},{"pid":"29ca9902e4c9efa92c8dbb51608696239ff45bdc","tid":419074,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi